  <slide>
    <title>Mission Statement</title>
    <contents>
      <p><em>The mission of the DRES Accessible IT Group is to research, promote and facilitate the application of universal design principles to online learning and information and communications technologies (ICT) through education, collaboration, evaluation, and outreach, with the objective of ensuring the comprehensive inclusion of students with disabilities in the Illinois Experience.</em></p>
    </contents>
